est. Its a wonderful virutal world thatwe live in. Its a place where we all can assume alter egos... If we are weak in that thing we call &quot;Real Life&quot; in our little world, we can be strong. If we are shy, we can be outgoing. If we are quiet, wecan be outspoken. All these things we can do in the safety and peace from our homes, quietly tucked away from the hardships and pain that are out there in the world.<br>
In this game we have our own petty squabbles. We bicker over 1's and 0's, or who said what. We fight about things that seem like the bigggest of deals. We squabble about honor and legitamacy. Just recently we spoke of gatheing in Orlando to meeet the people who seem so close to us, but that we have never met.<br>
<br>
And today, Real Life asserts itself to us.<br>
<br>
What I ask, not as Gahhl Blaadur, the self proclaimed, &quot;Official Organ of Infinitus Vindicat&quot;, not as a Shadowknight, not even as an EQ palyer, but as an American, is to KEEP LIVING YOUR LIFE. Terrorism, and the attack we all suffered today works only on fear. Do NOT give in. Even though it may be scary, do NOT give up your faith. When see the image of the plane arcing toward that building; let it anger you, let it inspire you to do something toward a fellow American, but do NOT let it break your spirit. Stand strong, and tell ALL those who would threaten you and yours that you are NOT afraid. Continue with your life. Mourn those you lost, but NEVER be scared. We are THE greatest country on the planet. When others are in need, America is there. When the weak need to be defended, America is there. <br>
So please, help your fellow American. Donate blood... Donate time... Donate money... Do what ever you can to help, but don't give up, and never give in... if there is anything that unites us as a people... as humans, its that type of spirit.<br>
<br>
